<div class="slide bg-offwhite" data-document-role="page" data-label="C1 · Finding 2">
  <div class="counter">4/9</div>
  <div class="safe">
    <h2 class="headline h-slide">The same routine, same order, same words becomes a signal the body <span class="underline-pink">learns to trust</span>.</h2>
  </div>
