<div class="slide caption-page" data-document-role="page" data-label="C1 · Caption (copy/paste)">
  <div class="caption-flag">Caption (not for posting)</div>
  <div class="caption-body">If mornings feel like a battle, it might not be about the socks or the cereal. When the day is predictable, your child's stress system gets to soften. Same order, same words, same rhythm tells their body it is safe. Pick one transition this week and keep it identical. Save this for the next chaotic morning.</div>
